Sentencas: Sample preparation and scanning electron microscopy imaging methods were des-eloped to characterize solid-oxide fuel cell anodes made out of a nickel-yttria-stabilized zirconia porous cermet.
Titulo: Rapid Preparation and SEM Microstructural Characterization of Nickel-Yttria-Stabilized Zirconia Cermets

Sentencas: The sample preparation uses only tripod polishing and does not require any resin impregnation.
Titulo: Rapid Preparation and SEM Microstructural Characterization of Nickel-Yttria-Stabilized Zirconia Cermets

Sentencas: To overcome surface damages induced by polishing, as well as to increase contrast between phases, high acceleration voltages were used.
Titulo: Rapid Preparation and SEM Microstructural Characterization of Nickel-Yttria-Stabilized Zirconia Cermets

Sentencas: The method gave results of a small systematic increase of the measured nickel proportion due to imaging conditions.
Titulo: Rapid Preparation and SEM Microstructural Characterization of Nickel-Yttria-Stabilized Zirconia Cermets

Sentencas: A quick image analyzing method is also presented.
Titulo: Rapid Preparation and SEM Microstructural Characterization of Nickel-Yttria-Stabilized Zirconia Cermets
